'''''Public Money & Management''''' (PMM) is an [[academic journal]] which was established by the [[Chartered Institute of Public Finance and Accountancy]] (CIPFA) in 1981 as ''Public Money'' to be "an independent journal to promote discussion of public sector policy making". The journal obtained its current title in 1988. The journal is published by [[Taylor & Francis]].

